# WhyML - Modular YAML Manifest Ecosystem

```bash
 ██╗    ██╗██╗  ██╗██╗   ██╗███╗   ███╗██╗     
 ██║    ██║██║  ██║╚██╗ ██╔╝████╗ ████║██║     
